---
title: Quickfire Beef Enchiladas with Homemade Ranchero Beans
description: We've been trying out a few new techniques in the test kitchen and this one has become a favourite - by mashing up most of the kidney beans instead of adding them whole, you suddenly add a rich, creamy texture to sauces. Keep a few whole ones back for texture too... arriba!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quickfire-beef-enchiladas-a9805d29.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/quickfire-beef-enchiladas-8be12496.pdf
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
  calories: 898 kcal
  fat: 37 g
  carbohydrates: 95 g
  protein: 50 g
  fiber: 18 g
  sodium: 1173 mg
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
